[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cardiff police hunt driver of flipped car

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police are hunting a driver who fled after flipping a car onto its roof on a busy Cardiff street.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Two other vehicles were damaged when the car overturned on Broadway in the Adamsdown area of the city.
The incident happened at about 05:15 BST on Saturday.
South Wales Police said it appeared nobody was injured in the crash, and the vehicle was removed and the road reopened by about 06:30.
